<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/00_Basics/MS_Content/hr/hr-landing-page.md" sourcestartlinenumber="90"><a href="localizations/noam-usa-track-time-for-fmla.md" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/00_Basics/MS_Content/hr/hr-landing-page.md" sourcestartlinenumber="90">Track time off for the Family and Medical Leave Act (FMLA)</a></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="gather-information-using-questionnaires" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/00_Basics/MS_Content/hr/hr-landing-page.md" sourcestartlinenumber="92">Gather information using questionnaires</h2>
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/00_Basics/MS_Content/hr/hr-landing-page.md" sourcestartlinenumber="94">You can design and administer questionnaires to gather information that's used for a variety of purposes. The Questionnaire feature lets you design and create questionnaires. When a questionnaire is ready, you distribute it broadly or to a specific set of respondents to complete. After the respondents provide their answers, you can review and analyze the results.</p>
